\c 87
\s Mbiri yelioni
\s Pisarema ravanakomana vaKora; rwiyo.
\p
\v 871 Nheyo dzake dziri pamakomo matsvene.
\p
\v 2 Jehovha anoda masuo elioni Kupfuura pose panogara Jakobho.
\p
\v 3 Zvinhu zvakanakisa zvinotaurwa pamusoro pako,
\s Iwe guta raMwari.
\p
\v 4 Rahabhi neBhabhironi ndichati vari pakati pavanondiziva;
\s "Tarirai, Firisitia, neTire, neItiopia; Munhu uyu akazvarirwako."
\p
\v 5 Zvirokwazvo, pamusoro pelioni vachati,
\s "Uyu nouyo vakazvarirwamo; Naiye Wokumusorosoro amene acharisimbisa."
\s achaverenga, pakunyora kwake ndudzi, achiti,
\s "Munhu uyu akazvarirwako."
\p
\v 7 Vanoimba navanotamba, vachati,
\s "Matsime angu ose ari mauri."
